               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<center><div class=\"first_steps_reflection_parent\"><div class=\"first_steps_reflection question_mark\"><i class=\"fa-solid fa-brain\"></i></div><div class=\"first_steps_reflection\"><b>Reflection 1: I am the beginning...</b><br /><br />Given this initial explanation, which species would have been the first to manufacture manual tools?</div></div></center>",
